Wild Die rolls:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code text"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-1" name="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;output [highest of [explode d4] and [explode d6]] named "d4 or wild die"
&lt;a id="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-2" name="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;output [highest of [explode d6] and [explode d6]] named "d6 or wild die"
&lt;a id="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-3" name="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;output [highest of [explode d8] and [explode d6]] named "d8 or wild die"
&lt;a id="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-4" name="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;output [highest of [explode d10] and [explode d6]] named "d10 or wild die"
&lt;a id="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-5" name="rest_code_64725e6c3a214ae5a1951017b291b8b2-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;output [highest of [explode d12] and [explode d6]] named "d12 or wild die"
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here's a link to the &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://anydice.com/program/23126/at_least"&gt;results&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>anydice.com</category><category>rpg</category><category>savage worlds</category><guid>https://tkurtbond.github.io/posts/2021/07/04/savage-worlds-wild-die-rolls-at-anydicecom/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 04 Jul 2021 19:51:54 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>